cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CY 

This paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) and machine learning techniques applied to patent claims. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with NLP and related topics. The paper also discusses the use of Amazon Mechanical Turk for dataset collection, which falls under the category of crowdsourcing and human computation, making cs.IR (Information Retrieval) another likely category. The paper also discusses the use of machine learning techniques, making cs.LG (Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) likely categories. Finally, the paper deals with patent processing, which involves legal and regulatory aspects, making cs.CY (Computers and Society) a possible category as well.
